            "description": "## Get Authenticated User\n\nRetrieves the profile of a specific user by their ID. Typically used to fetch the currently logged-in user's details after login.\n\n**Access:** Admin, Analyst, Viewer (authenticated users only — users can only fetch their own profile unless Admin)\n\n### Path Variables\n| Variable | Type | Required | Description |\n|----------|------|----------|-------------|\n| userId | string | Yes | MongoDB ObjectId of the user (e.g., `69cd709ef6d0d02290c9de6e`) |\n\n### Notes\n- Requires a valid JWT cookie (`token`)\n- Non-admin users can only access their own profile\n\n### Response Examples\n\n**200 OK**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"_id\": \"69cd709ef6d0d02290c9de6e\",\n    \"name\": \"Suraj Sharma\",\n    \"email\": \"suraj.sharma@example.com\",\n    \"role\": \"admin\",\n    \"status\": \"active\",\n    \"createdAt\": \"2026-04-04T10:00:00.000Z\",\n    \"updatedAt\": \"2026-04-04T12:00:00.000Z\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**401 Unauthorized** – Missing or invalid token\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Authentication required. Please log in.\"\n}\n```\n\n**403 Forbidden** – Accessing another user's profile without Admin role\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Access denied. You can only view your own profile.\"\n}\n```\n\n**404 Not Found**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"User not found\"\n}\n```\n\n**500 Internal Server Error**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"message\": \"Internal server error. Please try again later.\"\n}\n```"
